   "body" : "There is a common misconception that the block count returned by the blockchain rpcs includes the genesis block. See for example the discussion in https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/16292#issuecomment-506303256.\r\n\r\nHowever, it really returns the height, which is `0` for the genesis block.\r\n\r\nSo clarify that and also remove the misleading \"longest blockchain\" comment.\r\n\r\nFinally, fix the wallet test that incorrectly used this rpc.",
